[Main]
Name=TE_FAR_RIGHT
Type=Constant
Subtype=Macro
Header Files=textedit.h
Definition=#define TE_FAR_RIGHT (0xFFFF)
See Also=TE_open

[Description]
A constant defining the last cursor position in <A HREF="$$LINK(TE_open)">TE_open</A>.

[Explanation]
Set the parameter <I>cur_offset</I> in <A HREF="$$LINK(TE_open)">TE_open</A> to TE_FAR_RIGHT will place the edit cursor after the last character in the edit buffer.